data.description: Nestled in the serene community of Sandy Creek this picturesque home  offers a unique opportunity to live in harmony with nature. Enjoy the peaceful serenity of a pristine pond view from the comfort of your own home.  Wake up to the beauty of a glistening water right outside your window, and unwind with breathtaking sunset vistas in the evenings.  This Townhome has been remodeled and ready to be moved into!   Short term rentals are allowed, which makes this a great investment opportunity!   Don't miss this incredible opportunity to make this haven your own. Schedule a viewing today and experience the tranquility and natural beauty right from your doorstep!
